{"tid":1523742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(勇武意見）企後排/和理非 介唔介意都幫手scout","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T16:17:26.000Z","uid":128348,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6b91f6960cfeca8cb34be8d3d3713c33c465eb09","tid":1523742,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:07:46.000Z","msg":"其實前排頂緊果陣<br />\n我見好多人企後面都唔知做緊咩咁 <br />\n係唔知自己可以做d 咩 等人俾order 咁<br />\n<br />\n介唔介意都幫手 scout 下 <br />\n<br />\n睇下咩位應該留意<br />\n睇手睇水<br />\n<br />\n今晚9點果陣 銅鑼灣前線其實已經退緊 <br />\n但突然有班龜係側邊衝出黎 <br />\n好明顯係兜路包我地<br />\n<br />\n好多人都頭也不回咁走<br />\n我明白你會驚 每個人既受壓能力都唔一樣<br />\n但可唔可以幫幫平時走最後果班<br />\n今日佢咁包 走最後果d 都有人比人捉<br />\n<br />\n如果你肯幫手scout <br />\n1. 前線就可以有多d 資訊幾時應該退 應該set 邊到rb<br />\n2. 一定唔會咁迫 多d buffer位 係需要時比前線閪奔<br />\n<br />\n唔該你"},{"pid":"09daabdc68a0ce422dd38da6fbc5f892a9a3ecc7","tid":1523742,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:08:01.000Z","msg":"9 1 機場"},{"pid":"9dd6beb8cc169609bfb45a46e98787dd9a9bd764","tid":1523742,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:08:16.000Z","msg":"9 1 機場"},{"pid":"77148ca8e2c7a502a489b693f94ef26082655107","tid":1523742,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"9 1 機場"},{"pid":"b6cfc6a1122e2b49b0bf1bd94a152928c53504c6","tid":1523742,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f737e8099792becdcd97681cb9b0166108b18daf","tid":1523742,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:08:37.000Z","msg":"9 1 機場"},{"pid":"abfcbdb409593e59507edc01fc2703d39e748c55","tid":1523742,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:08:47.000Z","msg":"9 1 機場"},{"pid":"c3fa2352288d102a54bced2b93799f4d164c5c6f","tid":1523742,"uid":128348,"like"