br />\n等狗鐵永久不能運作 齊齊唔洗返工 仲正過塞機場<br />\n唔通爆黑社會麻雀館 就係極限? 黑社會定係狗鐵(政府)仆街D?<br />\n塞鐵已經無用 要直接令全港狗鐵收皮<br />\n今晚咁既下場 就係狗鐵害既 其實都唔止今晚<br />\n你估落去屌D職員有用? 咪撚玩喇<br />\n跳閘? 加價都賺返有突<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n站內鋪頭日日唔敢開 <br />\n列車運作唔到 無人坐 齊齊唔洗返工 一係排到仆街去坐巴士<br />\n無人敢再落廣告<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>清洗每個狗鐵站 拆鐵行動! 旺角行先!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d3146b461baea5a460c727d1e351ce3d9ea4ac6b","tid":1523742,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:14:12.000Z","msg":"9 1 機場"},{"pid":"7ea8978a81c77388ab13a5922501d35a4aad0631","tid":1523742,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:14:29.000Z","msg":"9 1 機場"},{"pid":"3ccfc7a119dec8bc860d74319c0ec129100c4447","tid":1523742,"uid":136457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:14:50.000Z","msg":"希望前線肯接收資訊"},{"pid":"215d2795830ccba47f64889036200374a03b832f","tid":1523742,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:15:16.000Z","msg":"9 1 機場"},{"pid":"fbd255c89f7ac1adec8d2654729f1f84d7dd83b0","tid":1523742,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:15:46.000Z","msg":"9 1 機場"},{"pid":"5f0596b373ecf3a6954887f722ff50acca02b44c","tid":1523742,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:15:56.000Z","msg":"9 1 機場"},{"pid":"436d32556c55e21fdac7a3ef41485e773833dda3","tid":1523742,"uid":37929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:15:57.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"14d83f17dbe27392a242c88bd40522209fc27a9a","tid":1523742,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:16:06.000Z","msg":"9 1 機場"},{"pid":"88582720e286e7d2ebda2bd18e196f1334b510fd","tid":1523742,"uid":128348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"9 1 機場"},{"pid":"12638f572e0cf1e3e9de3f6e4d50d568d4